    issue.specials: data-driven spec-proc assignment (replaces lib/misc/specials.lst + InitSpecProcs).
    Mobs are grouped UNDER each special (the special id is an ESpecial enum token):
        <special id="kRent"><mob vnum="4022"/><mob vnum="4001"/></special>
    A mob may appear under several <special> blocks (banker + innkeeper, trainer + merchant).
    id: kRent kMail kBank kHorse kExchange kTorc kMercenary kOutfit kPuff.  vnum: positive integer.
